I dont want there to
be that hesitation.

00:35:08.160 --> 00:35:09.460
I want... (snaps his fingers)

00:35:09.460 --> 00:35:10.630
There it is.

00:35:10.630 --> 00:35:11.960
Ta-da!

00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:14.130
"No, no, no. Go ahead
and put my coat"

00:35:14.130 --> 00:35:15.860
"in the overhead
for me, please."

00:35:15.860 --> 00:35:19.260
FARCHIONE: The one
moment that really stuck
out for me was the moment

00:35:19.260 --> 00:35:21.860
at which she was
willing to get up.

00:35:21.860 --> 00:35:23.960
"She didnt want to do
it, but she did it."

00:35:23.960 --> 00:35:25.330
"You know, I mean,
she really..."

