"She knew it was the
right thing to do,"

00:35:27.330 --> 00:35:29.330
and she committed to it.

00:35:29.330 --> 00:35:30.930
Excellent.

00:35:30.930 --> 00:35:34.260
That was the point
at which I felt

00:35:34.260 --> 00:35:37.360
very good about her ability
to overcome this problem.

00:35:37.360 --> 00:35:40.530
Youre getting there.
Youre getting there.

