Slowly but surely.

00:35:41.760 --> 00:35:43.430
I... I dont know.

00:35:43.430 --> 00:35:46.000
"Im going to say, actually, um,"

00:35:46.000 --> 00:35:48.360
"I dont think its as
slowly as you, uh,"

00:35:48.360 --> 00:35:49.900
you might imagine.

00:35:49.900 --> 00:35:52.060
Youre doing... youre
doing a fantastic job.

00:35:52.060 --> 00:35:54.860
Absolutely fantastic.

00:35:54.860 --> 00:35:56.300
Thank you very much. Excuse me.

00:35:56.300 --> 00:35:57.860
I might see you again soon.

00:35:57.860 --> 00:35:59.560
Thank you.

00:35:59.560 --> 00:36:03.760
See you guys.

00:36:03.760 --> 00:36:05.030
All right.

00:36:05.030 --> 00:36:06.200
I like them.

00:36:06.200 --> 00:36:07.230
"Its like the, uh..."

00:36:07.230 --> 00:36:08.630
"Yeah, they were
nice, right? Right."

